{
  "id": "adv_main_02_12_04",
  "title": "東京編2章34話",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_lesson-02-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": null
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_studio-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――セミファイナル数日前。サニピの特訓中",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――A few days before the semi-finals‚ during Sunny Peace's training.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_12_04/sud_vo_adv_main_02_12_04-ktn001.m4a",
      "text": "凄い、さくら達……\n見違えるぐらいダンスのキレが良くなってる",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Amazing‚ Sakura and the others…\nYour dancing has gotten so much sharper.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 14.0333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_12_04/sud_vo_adv_main_02_12_04-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "あぁ。それに、歌もバッチリだ\n踊りながらでも、音が全然ブレていない",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah. And your singing is perfect.\nEven while dancing‚ your voices aren't wavering at all.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 21.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_12_04/sud_vo_adv_main_02_12_04-ktn002.m4a",
      "text": "これが、特訓の成果なんですね。でも……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So this is the result of your training. But…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 24.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_12_04/sud_vo_adv_main_02_12_04-rio001.m4a",
      "text": "……ええ、このままじゃ\nスリクスには絶対に届かない",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Yeah‚ at this rate‚\nthey'll never reach ⅢX.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 33.5333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_tension-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 35.9666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_12_04/sud_vo_adv_main_02_12_04-ktn003.m4a",
      "text": "はい。今のサニピは強いです。悔しいくらいに……\nそれでもサニピが勝利した画が、浮かばないんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes. Sunny Peace is strong now. Frustratingly so…\nBut I still can't imagine them winning.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 43.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_12_04/sud_vo_adv_main_02_12_04-rui001.m4a",
      "text": "……私も同感です。確かに実力はぐんと底上げされた\nでもそれだけじゃ足りない",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…I agree. They've certainly improved their skills dramatically‚\nbut that's not enough.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 54.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_12_04/sud_vo_adv_main_02_12_04-rui002.m4a",
      "text": "スリクスに勝つには、あの人達に圧倒されない\n強くて太い芯が必要なんだと思う",
      "translations": {
        "en": "To beat ⅢX‚ to not be overwhelmed by them‚\nI think they need a strong and firm core.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 60.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_12_04/sud_vo_adv_main_02_12_04-rio002.m4a",
      "text": "そうね。あの子達にとって、アイドルとはなんなのか\nどんなアイドルになりたいのか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You're right. What being an idol means to them‚\nwhat kind of idols they want to be.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 69.9666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_12_04/sud_vo_adv_main_02_12_04-rio003.m4a",
      "text": "スリクスにあって、あの子達に欠けているものよ\nそれを手に入れて、やっと勝負の舞台に立てる",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's what ⅢX has that they lack.\nThey need to gain that‚ and only then can they stand on the battlefield.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 77.1666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_12_04/sud_vo_adv_main_02_12_04-ktn004.m4a",
      "text": "……だから私達は……\nその答えを見つけられなかったから……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…That's why we…\nbecause we couldn't find that answer…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 84.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_12_04/sud_vo_adv_main_02_12_04-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "でもそれは、外野がとやかく言ったり\n特訓で見つけられるものじゃない",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But that's not something outsiders can talk about or\nsomething you can find through training.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 91.1333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_12_04/sud_vo_adv_main_02_12_04-rio004.m4a",
      "text": "ええ。ファイナル、スリクスとの対決までに\n見つからなければ……負けるわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah. If they don't find it before the finals‚ before the battle with ⅢX…\nthey'll lose.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 97.1666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_lesson-02-evening.webp",
      "bgName": "stage02",
      "startTime": 101.2666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_trouble-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 101.5
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_12_04/sud_vo_adv_main_02_12_04-skr001.m4a",
      "text": "はぁ、はぁ、はぁ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Huff‚ huff‚ huff…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 102.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_12_04/sud_vo_adv_main_02_12_04-hrk001.m4a",
      "text": "みんな、今日はもう、この辺にしておきましょ？\nこれ以上は、ライブ前に体を壊しちゃうから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Everyone‚ let's stop here for today‚ okay?\nAny more than this‚ and you'll hurt yourselves before the live.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 111.6666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_12_04/sud_vo_adv_main_02_12_04-rei001.m4a",
      "text": "そうね。みんな、ちゃんとストレッチして……\n……さくら？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You're right. Everyone‚ make sure to stretch…\n…Sakura?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 121.0333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_12_04/sud_vo_adv_main_02_12_04-skr002.m4a",
      "text": "え？　あ、うん。ストレッチだよね\n怜ちゃん、一緒にやろう？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Huh? Ah‚ yeah. Stretching‚ right?\nRei-chan‚ let's do it together.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 125.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_12_04/sud_vo_adv_main_02_12_04-rei002.m4a",
      "text": "……何か思っていることがあるなら、隠さずに言って\nずっと思い詰めた顔されると、気になるから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…If you have something on your mind‚ don't hide it and tell me.\nIt bothers me when you keep making that troubled face.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 132.7433333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_12_04/sud_vo_adv_main_02_12_04-skr003.m4a",
      "text": "あはは……やっぱり、バレちゃったね。ごめん\n……あのね、私、ずっと考えてることがあるの",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ahaha… I guess you saw through me. Sorry.\n…You see‚ there's something I've been thinking about.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 143.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_12_04/sud_vo_adv_main_02_12_04-skr004.m4a",
      "text": "私達、どんなアイドルになりたいんだろう\n私達にとってのアイドルって、なんなのかな、って",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What kind of idols do we want to be?\nWhat does being an idol mean to us?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 153.1333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_12_04/sud_vo_adv_main_02_12_04-szk001.m4a",
      "text": "……えっと、哲学？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Um‚ philosophy?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 157.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_serious-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 163.1
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_12_04/sud_vo_adv_main_02_12_04-skr005.m4a",
      "text": "そういうんじゃないよ！　ただ……ライブバトルでの\n勝ち負けは、私達にとっての全てじゃない",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's not like that! It's just…\nwinning or losing in a live battle isn't everything to us.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 165.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_12_04/sud_vo_adv_main_02_12_04-skr006.m4a",
      "text": "自分達らしい形でライブを楽しむことが\nサニーピースの強みだ、って思ってきた。だけど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I thought our strength was to enjoy live performances in our own way.\nBut…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 173.31,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_12_04/sud_vo_adv_main_02_12_04-chs001.m4a",
      "text": "わ、私はその考え方も十分\nサニピらしいって思ってたんだけど、ち、違うの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I-I thought that way of thinking was plenty\nlike Sunny Peace‚ b-but is it different?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 182.5666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_12_04/sud_vo_adv_main_02_12_04-rei003.m4a",
      "text": "確かに考え方は、私達らしくていいと思う\nでもさくらが言いたいのは、きっともっと先にある……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I think that way of thinking is like us‚\nbut what Sakura wants to say is surely something further ahead…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 192.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_12_04/sud_vo_adv_main_02_12_04-szk002.m4a",
      "text": "サニーピースの、着地点\nあるいは……明確な、チェックポイント",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sunny Peace's landing point.\nOr… a clear checkpoint.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 200.4666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_12_04/sud_vo_adv_main_02_12_04-hrk002.m4a",
      "text": "確かに、着地点はちゃんと見えていた方がいいわね\n無計画な登山ほど、危ないものはないもの",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's true‚ it's better to have a clear landing point.\nThere's nothing more dangerous than unplanned mountain climbing.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 210.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_12_04/sud_vo_adv_main_02_12_04-skr007.m4a",
      "text": "うん。スリクスはしっかりと目的を持ってるでしょ？\nそれが何かは、教えてくれなかったけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah. ⅢX has a firm purpose‚ right?\nThey wouldn't tell me what it was‚ though.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 220.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage03",
      "startTime": 225.1666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage03",
      "startTime": 225.1666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_sad-01.m4a",
