      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_lesson-02-evening.webp",
      "bgName": "stage02",
      "startTime": 245.4333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_12_04/sud_vo_adv_main_02_12_04-chs002.m4a",
      "text": "そっか……迷わずに、正しい道を突き進めている\nだからあんなに、自信があって……強いんだね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I see… They're forging ahead on the right path without hesitation.\nThat's why they're so confident… and strong.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 252.6666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_12_04/sud_vo_adv_main_02_12_04-skr008.m4a",
      "text": "勝ち負けは抜きにライブを楽しむのはもちろんだけど\n私達は、アイドルとして何を成し遂げたいのか……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Of course‚ we enjoy our lives regardless of winning or losing‚ but\nwhat do we want to achieve as idols…?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 262.0433333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_12_04/sud_vo_adv_main_02_12_04-skr009.m4a",
      "text": "それが見つからないと\nスリクスに並ぶステージは作れない気がするんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I feel like we can't create a stage that rivals ⅢX\nunless we find that.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 268.9333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_12_04/sud_vo_adv_main_02_12_04-chs004.m4a",
      "text": "……難しいね\n私達それぞれには、目標ってあるけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…That's difficult.\nWe each have our own goals‚ but",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 275.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_12_04/sud_vo_adv_main_02_12_04-hrk004.m4a",
      "text": "確かに、今までサニーピース全体で向き合って\n考えたことは、なかった気がするわね",
      "translations": {
