      "text": "……ごめんね、急にこんなこと言い出して\nもっと前に話し合うべきだったよね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…I'm sorry for suddenly bringing this up.\nWe should've talked about this sooner.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 290.5666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
