      "text": "それは否定しないけど、逆に、今で良かったって思うわ\n今この時じゃなかったら、考えもしなかっただろうし",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I won't deny that‚ but conversely‚ I think it's good that we're talking about it now.\nIf it weren't for this moment‚ we wouldn't have even thought about it.",
        "id": ""
